Ssh
=========

Install Notes
-------------

  1. host should be the hostname or ip address of a server that is listening for this ssh connection.
  2. port should be the port number that the server is running on.  
  3. user should be the username of the account on the host.
  4. key should be the RSA private key used to authenticate to the server.


Developer Notes
---------------

data
  - host
  - port
  - user
  - key

payload
  - refer to docs/github_payload

Deployment Notes
----------------

The private key should NOT include the header or footer i.e.(-----BEGIN RSA PRIVATE KEY----- and -----END RSA PRIVATE KEY-----)